text: The 2017 Liga 3 West Sulawesi season is the third edition of Liga 3 West Sulawesi is a qualifying round of the 2017 Liga 3. Mamuju Utama FC are the defending champions. ==Teams== This season there are 7 clubs in West Sulawesi become participants. They are: # Persimaju Mamuju # PS Sandeq Polman # Balanipa Mandar FC # TSL AKO FC # Gasman Majene # PS Matra # OTP37 FC == References == Category:2017 in Indonesian football Category:West Sulawesi
